data.description: Motivated Seller, priced to sell, moving out of state for workl. Bring your best offer! Welcome Home to everything you have been looking for in this fabulous and immaculately maintained beauty nestled in the sought-after Castlebrooke community! The foyer welcomes you by the formal dining room and large office and leads to the large kitchen featuring granite countertops, center island/breakfast bar, and dining area all overlooking the welcoming fireside family room highlighted by a wall of windows, high ceiling. This beauty has been upgraded with beautiful Luxury Vinyl planks thru-out the first and second floors, stairs, and hallways, the rooms have carpets. Large owner suite, with walk in closets, separate shower jacuzzi tub, three large rooms upstairs, one room has a full bathroom and two share a full bath. Full stubbed unfinished basement, with fenced backyard, enclosed back porch and walk out deck. A Must See..!
